    <h1>Primary Category (GBP)</h1>
    <p class="description">The single most important classification you assign to your Google Business Profile listing. It tells Google the core nature of your business and carries <strong>more weight for local pack rankings</strong> than any other GBP element — including reviews and proximity.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
